title: Double Berry Cobbler A sweet summery dessert. | 2 Single-Serve Cakes
description: This comforting cobbler may be mini in size, but it sure is mighty in flavor. A layer of sweet berry filling is covered with a fluffy crumb topping for tantalizing textural contrast. When you want to dig in, all you have to do is...nothing! Enjoy cold, at room temp, or warmed up in the microwave. (Psst—we highly recommend serving with a scoop of vanilla ice cream on top.)

