2 unit Double Berry Cobbler

Keep frozen or refrigerated until ready to eat; best if used within 7 days. If frozen, thaw in the refrigerator (at 40 degrees) overnight or for 2-3 hours at room temperature before eating. Enjoy cold, at room temperature, or heat in the microwave. **MICROWAVE:** Remove and discard plastic wrapping. Microwave thawed product until warmed through, 30-45 seconds. Do not overheat.